<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Our Services - Visionary Frames</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .service-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .service {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: 0.4s;
        }

        .service:hover {
            background: #27ae60;
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .service h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .service p {
            font-size: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Our Services</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">"Your vision, our precision."</p>
        <div class="service-list">
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Custom Eyewear</h3>
                <p>Get tailored glasses that fit your face perfectly and complement your unique style.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Blue Light Protection</h3>
                <p>Protect your eyes from digital screens with our advanced blue light glasses collection.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
                <p>Need help choosing? Get a free style and vision consultation from our experts.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Worldwide Delivery</h3>
                <p>We ship globally, delivering premium eyewear directly to your doorstep.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>Virtual Try-On</h3>
                <p>Try your favorite frames online with our exclusive virtual try-on feature.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service">
                <h3>VIP Membership</h3>
                <p>Enjoy special discounts, early access to collections, and premium customer support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
